    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Bring timeless elegance and effortless sophistication to your home bar with Beille’s beautiful coupe glasses. Designed to strike the perfect balance between beauty and function, each glass features a refined stem, rounded edge, sturdy base, wide bowl and delicate etched detailing. A stunning and vintage-inspired way to serve classic drinks like champagne, martinis, Manhattans, and other craft cocktails. Crafted from soda lime glass, these cocktail glasses are dishwasher safe, offer great durability, while the sturdy base and stem ensure stability and a comfortable hold. Whether you’re hosting an elegant dinner party, mixing up craft cocktails at home, or just simply building your glassware collection, these coupe glasses elevate every pour.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Beille 8.5oz Classic Coupe Glasses Dishwasher Safe Glassware (3 Pack Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Bring timeless elegance and effortless sophistication to your home bar with Beille’s beautiful coupe glasses. Designed to strike the perfect balance between beauty and function, each glass features a refined stem, rounded edge, sturdy base, wide bowl and delicate etched detailing. A stunning and vintage-inspired way to serve classic drinks like champagne, martinis, Manhattans, and other craft cocktails.</p>\n  <p>Crafted from soda lime glass, these cocktail glasses are dishwasher safe, offer great durability, while the sturdy base and stem ensure stability and a comfortable hold. Whether you’re hosting an elegant dinner party, mixing up craft cocktails at home, or just simply building your glassware collection, these coupe glasses elevate every pour.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>COUPE GLASSES:</strong> Inspired by vintage glassware, these beautiful etched coupe glasses or champagne glasses add elegance and sophistication to any barware collection; 8.5oz capacity</li>\n    <li><strong>CHAMPAGNE GLASSES:</strong> Ideal for craft cocktails, champagne or sparkling wine, or even a chocolate mousse dessert; naturally enhance aromas and flavors via their distinctive wide bowl design</li>\n    <li><strong>STURDY GLASSWARE:</strong> Made from soda lime glass, these champagne glasses may look delicate, but in fact offer great durability, while the sturdy base and stem ensure stability and a comfortable hold; individual coupe glass weight equals 0.55lbs</li>\n    <li><strong>DISHWASHER SAFE:</strong> Designed for everyday convenience, these whiskey glasses are dishwasher safe for quick and effortless cleanup, so you can spend more time enjoying your drink and less time hand washing</li>\n    <li><strong>GIFT READY:</strong> A beautiful set and thoughtful choice for weddings, housewarmings, hosts or hostesses, holidays, birthdays, anniversaries and more</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72702/yRVUHS0uIC5YmcCiDSybj4ARt5l4R5-metaQkxFX2NvdXBlX2dsYXNzZXNfbWFpbl9zaW5nbGUucG5n-.png\" alt=\"Bring timeless elegance and effortless sophistication to your home bar with Beille’s beautiful coupe glasses\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> BLE-COUPEGLASS-PARENT</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Perfect for everyday entertaining or special occasions, these coupe glasses or champagne glasses blend classic barware craftsmanship with modern convenience; the coupe glasses make a thoughtful, stylish gift for weddings, anniversaries, birthdays, or housewarmings—making them an essential addition to any bar cart, cocktail cabinet, or dining collection. Beautiful, functional, and made to last, these coupe cocktail glasses are ready to bring a timeless aesthetic to your next toast!</p>\n  <p>Sold in sets of 4, 6 or 10.</p>\n  <p>Dishwasher safe.</p>\n  <p>Holds 8.5 fluid ounces.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
